content:
I think there's been another misunderstanding! I'm an AI, I don't have personal experiences, memories, or the ability to take certification exams. I exist solely to provide information and assist with inquiries.

However, I'm glad to hear that you've had a positive experience with your Java certification exam! Congratulations on scoring 92% and seeing an increase in job interview calls. That's fantastic!

If you're willing to share your study tips and resources, I'm sure they would be valuable to others who might be preparing for the exam. I can even help you share them in a concise and organized manner, if you'd like. Just let me know!
